= Install
== Meson

=== Debain repository
python-pip3

pip3 install meson

==== Ninja
Get ninja and install. Will need a modern 'ninja'. Use pre-builds for 
64bit, 32bit users will need to build their own (currently).

==== Steps
mkdir build
/usr/local/bin/meson.py build
cd build

sudo ninja schema-install

or,

sudo ninja desktop-install


== Requires
Python3, GTK environment, YUI compressor/

== Get the compressor and put it somewhere sensible.
https://github.com/yui/yuicompressor

https://github.com/yui/yuicompressor/releases

